content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8026.00 - General

State Regulations
(a) IR 390. The
northbound and southbound roadways of IR 390 between the Livingston-Monroe
county line and IR 490 in the City of Rochester and the Towns of Rush, Henrietta, Brighton, Chili and Gates. (b) IR 490. The eastbound and westbound
roadways of IR 490 between the Genesee-Monroe county line and the

Monroe-Ontario county line in the City of Rochester and the Towns of Riga, Chili, Gates, Brighton, Pittsford and Perinton. (c) IR 590. The northbound and southbound
roadways of IR 590 between IR 390 to IR 490 in the City of Rochester and Town
of Brighton. (d) Route 104. The
eastbound and westbound roadways of Route 104 between Maplewood Drive and the

Monroe-Wayne county line in the City of Rochester, Village of Webster, and

Towns of Irondequoit and Webster. (e) Route 390. The northbound and southbound
roadways of Route 390 between IR 490 and Latta Road, Route 18, in the Towns of

Gates and Greece. (f) Route 590. The northbound and southbound roadways of Route 590 between IR 490 and Route
104 in the City of Rochester and the Towns of Brighton and

Irondequoit. (g) IR 90. The
eastbound and westbound roadways of IR 90 between th Genesee-Monroe county line
and the Monroe-Ontario county line in the Towns of Wheatland, Chili, Henrietta, Pittsford and Mendon. Notes
